n-attachment-3786199" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3786199" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="2023 年诺丁山狂欢节。照片来源：HENRY NICHOLLS/AFP via Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/notting-hill-carnival-2023-@-2000-x-1270-HENRY-NICHOLLS_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3786199" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年诺丁山狂欢节。照片来源：HENRY NICHOLLS/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>大卫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/craig-david-announces-commitment-2025-uk-arena-tour-with-lemar-buy-tickets-3751629">最近宣布了 2025 年的巡演</a>。门票现已发售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcraig-david-tickets%2Fartist%2F703676" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买</a>。</p><p>演出日期从 2 月 2 日（星期日）开始，以利兹 First Direct Arena 的开幕之夜拉开帷幕，然后两晚后（2 月 4 日）在格拉斯哥的 Armadillo 场地继续演出。</p><p>从那里开始，本月剩余时间里，纽卡斯尔、米尔顿凯恩斯、布莱顿、卡迪夫和诺丁汉的演出将在曼彻斯特的 Co-Op Live 竞技场、伯明翰名胜世界竞技场、伯恩茅斯国际中心等地结束。最后是 2 月 20 日在伦敦举办的 The O2。</p><p>这位歌手凭借广受好评的首张专辑《Born To Do It》首次崭露头角，这张定义流派的唱片巩固了他在英国 R&amp;B 界的巨星地位。他最热门的歌曲之一仍然是 1999 年的歌曲“Re-Rewind”，这首歌后来成为英国车库的经典之作。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6VhJXeIdUX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,3